# Public docs feature

- Content from Postgres via `$lib/server/services/docs.ts`
- Only `published` documents visible to anonymous visitors; admins see draft preview with banner
- `/docs` index supports `?q=` search (Postgres `ilike`)
- `/docs/[slug]` renders markdown via `$lib/markdown.ts` (marked + DOMPurify)
- Sidebar groups published docs by category in `+layout.server.ts`
- `/docs/[slug]` shows a right TOC (page title + markdown H1/H2) at `lg+` via `DocsTableOfContents.svelte`
